# Adapt
Writing 101: know your audience. Adapt lets you tailor documents for different audiences [techie => using a simple text format]. [github => And it's hosted on GitHub!]

## Usage
To use adapt:

	adapt <target> c1 c2 ... cn

where `<target>` should have a corresponding file `<target>.adapt`. The result will be stored in `<target>`.

### Example
To adapt this README for GitHub:

	adapt README.md github
